Package prkmodel.repast

Class ParkinsonModelBuilder

java.lang.Object
prkmodel.repast.ParkinsonModelBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
repast.simphony.dataLoader.ContextBuilder<Object>
public class ParkinsonModelBuilder extends Object implements repast.simphony.dataLoader.ContextBuilder<Object>
Builder class for constructing the Parkinson's model in the Repast simulation environment. This class initializes the simulation context, space, network, and components of the nervous system.
